metadata.name: Mooncakes: Happy Mid Autumn Festival 2022 #3466
metadata.description:
To celebrate the Moon Festival with Mooncakes, we have created a quest to introduce everyone to fxhash. As part of that quest on mooncakes.fun, users are encouraged to mint this generative token.

This is a layered image composition using the Mooncakes site images on a 1920x1080 canvas. The image elements are randomly assigned position, scale, tint, and blur according to a ruleset which generates a Mid Autumn Festival scene made up of: Moon, Clouds, Stars, Lanterns, and Lotuses.

Special filters, shapes and colors are included as rare features, as well as a couple of surprises.

metadata.name: 1 Raffle Ticket "The Devils"
metadata.description:
This very special raffle ticket NFT is your chance to win one of three exclusive "The Devils" NFTs, sponsored by the "UP Community". Find us on Twitter at @upontezos.

To participate, simply send this raffle ticket to "upon.tez" or tz1NCUHMDakffJJPfNBzhoV8FYpCvPTDEjfa before 8 February, 2023.

But that's not all, hold a minimum of 1,000,000 UP tokens (~0.35$) in your wallet and TRIPLE your chances of winning!

You can easily purchase UP tokens using 3route.io (scan QR), Quipuswap or Plenty. 

- $UP is the first Tezos token that is designed to increase in value over time.
- Instead of paying miners or bakers. $UP pays you for upsorbing (staking) the coin.
- If less people upsorb, the average APY for all other upsorbers increases significantly.
- The longer you upsorb, the more you earn.

Don't miss your opportunity to take home one of the three exclusive "The Devils" NFTs up for grabs in this giveaway!
